channel.title: Need help!
channel.description: Hi there, I need help, I reset IE7 because it wouldnt shut down unless I used task manager, so I reset and now it works, but now I can't watch youtube vids, I installed java and adobe flash player, still it just keeps loading the vid. Please help.

item.title: Need help!
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

If the total image loads (you can see the black screen) that is an issue where your internet connection isn’t responding quickly. Restart your browser, and/or your modem if restarting your browser doesn’t work.

IE7 is not the best browser out there. Mozilla Firefox is a much better browser. If you just like the look of IE, there is a theme add-on that can be used if you wish.
